73
00:11:47,039 --> 00:11:48,480
[SPEAKER_00] Kad nisam bio na njegovoj strani.

74
00:11:50,639 --> 00:11:52,240
[SPEAKER_00] I evo, papinsto je bilo i tako.

75
00:11:52,639 --> 00:11:56,720
[SPEAKER_00] Miko Nose je mogao neke trice tu bacati, ali nije uspio.

76
00:11:57,039 --> 00:11:57,679
